    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_298_000163",
    "sentence": "裡人疾周者，入其姓名，遂被攝。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_298_000164",
    "sentence": "或勸周謁貴游以免，周曰：「往役，義也，謁貴游，不更辱乎！」",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "周",
        "label": "PER"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_012_298_000165",
